<% provide(:page_title, 'Help') %>

<div class="page-header">
	<h2>Help</h2>
</div>

<div class="help-content">
  
  <div class="help-section">
    <h3>CSV Import</h3>

    <ol>
  		<li>Ensure that your file has only the required fields and in the correct order</li>
  		<li>Export your file as a CSV with <strong>UTF-8 Encoding</strong></li>
  	</ol>
  </div>

    <!-- logs intro -->
  <div class="help-section">
      <h3>LOGS</h3>

      <p>Each log event belongs to a particular session and is associated directly</p>
      <p>The following items are logged:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Scrapes</li>
        <li>Pages</li>
        <li>Questions</li>
        <li>Answers</li>
      </ul>

    <!-- scrape logs description  -->
    <div class="help-section-sub">
      <h4>Scrape Logs</h4>

      <p>There are two different scraping events each with their respective logs</p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <h5>Initial Scrape Logs</h5>
          <p>This creates a log of the results of the initial scrape.</p>
          <p>Log Details</p>
          <ol>
            <li>Page URL (&amp; id)</li>
            <li>Start Date</li>
            <li>End Date</li>
            <li>Scrape Started on</li>
            <li>Scrape Completed on</li>
            <li>User</li>
            <li>Posts Collected</li>
            <li>Comments Collected</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>Regular Scrape Logs</h5>
          <p>This creates a log of the regular scrapes.</p>
          <p>Log Details</p>
          <ol>
            <li>Page URL (&amp; id)</li>
            <li>Scrape Started on</li>
            <li>Scrape Completed on</li>
            <li>Collected Posts</li>
            <li>Collected Comments</li>
            <li>Next Scrape</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>


